  <title>Ocultando contatos desconectados</title>

  <p>
    Normally, <app>Empathy</app> shows all your contacts: those that are online, 
    with which you can have a conversation, and also those that are offline. 
  </p>
  <p>Para esconder um ou mais contatos que estão desconectados:</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>From the <gui>Contact List</gui> window, choose <guiseq><gui>View</gui>
      <gui>Offline Contacts</gui></guiseq>, or press <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key>
      <key>H</key></keyseq>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>
        To show the offline contacts again, repeat the same procedure above.
      </p>
    </item>
  </steps>

